{"title":"SRAM Rival AXS derailleurs get the Kogel Kolossos OS ceramic pulley upgrade","link":"https://bikerumor.com/sram-rival-axs-derailleurs-get-the-kogel-kolossos-os-ceramic-pulley-upgrade/","date":1639252865000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/11145803/kogel-kolossos-rival-oversize-ceramic-bearing-derailleur-pulley-blue.jpg\" data-fancybox=\"\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"507\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/11145803/kogel-kolossos-rival-oversize-ceramic-bearing-derailleur-pulley-blue-800x507.jpg\" alt=\"kogel kolossos oversized sram rival derailleur pulley cage with ceramic bearings\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/11145803/kogel-kolossos-rival-oversize-ceramic-bearing-derailleur-pulley-blue-800x507.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/11145803/kogel-kolossos-rival-oversize-ceramic-bearing-derailleur-pulley-blue-297x188.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/11145803/kogel-kolossos-rival-oversize-ceramic-bearing-derailleur-pulley-blue-120x76.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/11145803/kogel-kolossos-rival-oversize-ceramic-bearing-derailleur-pulley-blue-768x486.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/11145803/kogel-kolossos-rival-oversize-ceramic-bearing-derailleur-pulley-blue.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></a><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-280703\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>With Zach giving the SRAM Rival eTap AXS group an honorable mention in <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/bikerumor-editors-choice-awards-2021-zachs-best-bikes-gear-picks/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">his Editor’s Choice roundup</a>, and my prior experience with <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/kogel-kolossus-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Kogel’s Kolossos pulley cage upgrade</a>, this new part makes the mid-level derailleur make more sense than ever.</p><p>Considering a Rival AXS rear derailleur <em>and</em> Kogel’s new Kolossos cage for it still comes in almost $100 less than a new SRAM Red AXS rear mech, it makes the ~$400 price tag for the cage little more palatable. Especially when you realize it comes with their free-spinning ceramic bearings.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/11145801/kogel-kolossos-rival-oversize-ceramic-bearing-derailleur-pulley-black2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/11145801/kogel-kolossos-rival-oversize-ceramic-bearing-derailleur-pulley-black2.jpg\" alt=\"kogel kolossos oversized sram rival derailleur pulley cage with ceramic bearings\" width=\"1219\" height=\"627\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/11145801/kogel-kolossos-rival-oversize-ceramic-bearing-derailleur-pulley-black2.jpg 1219w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/11145801/kogel-kolossos-rival-oversize-ceramic-bearing-derailleur-pulley-black2-297x153.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/11145801/kogel-kolossos-rival-oversize-ceramic-bearing-derailleur-pulley-black2-800x411.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/11145801/kogel-kolossos-rival-oversize-ceramic-bearing-derailleur-pulley-black2-120x62.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/11145801/kogel-kolossos-rival-oversize-ceramic-bearing-derailleur-pulley-black2-768x395.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1219px) 100vw, 1219px\"></a></p><p>This model is designed specifically for the 12-speed Rival AXS group, they offer different versions for Red and Force, which have a slightly different pivot location and tension hole placement. The features are the same, though, with a two-position tension spring adjustment so you can set it softer for road, or firmer for gravel, and 14-tooth upper and 19-tooth lower pulleys.</p><p>MSRP is $439, but through Dec. 31, 2021, it’s $399 with <a href=\"https://www.kogel.cc/collections/custom-product-configurator/products/sram-rival-etap-axs-oversized-derailleur-cage-custom?utm_source=Kogel+Bearings+News&amp;utm_campaign=d32374b3db-EMAIL_CAMPAIGN_RIVAL_KOLOSSOS_EMAIL_1&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_term=0_2ec7db00dc-d32374b3db-81805233&amp;mc_cid=d32374b3db&amp;mc_eid=66cd3c3a90\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">free customization</a> of pulley, stop pin, screws, and bearing cover colors, letting you mix and match all of those parts however you want. Choose from black, blue, red, gold, and raw.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.kogel.cc/collections/oversized-derailleur-cages/products/sram-rival-etap-axs-oversized-derailleur-cage-black?variant=42142486462678\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Kogel.cc</em></a></p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"236404c9e53ef41af98058d4090f8d2d044e20f290521a20527fad21d57e58fd","category":"Cycling"}